{
  "stem": "895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you think we're finished?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, don't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he began to cry, and I also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, they packed in-- the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we could go back to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were three girls.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were captured.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were shot to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the last of the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was blown up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was-- it was the last of the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anybody who came in from transport from September to November came from Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember 120 coming from Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all Dutch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I spoke with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had to come-- they didn't come to the [GERMAN], the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to undress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spoke with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said-- what did-- I didn't know nothing about Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They told me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, your brother and sisters were in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where did they go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, all of a sudden, we didn't see them anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were only two months there and they were gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I thought they were-- I thought also they were dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- they found out, this 120 had ancestors who were from England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they thought because they're from ancestors from England, they could be interned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two days later, all 120 were shot to death, all 120, every one of them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were taken away by the Sonderkommando, put them in the crematorium to be burned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the end of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they stop at the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anybody who came in was shot to death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that went on till December, 1944, when the Russians were coming forward, getting nearer and nearer-- Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't see no Russians at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
